
What is this?
==========================================
Sorta like Delicious, but just for you. Melicious lets you save and
manage your bookmarks.

How do I start?
==========================================
0. cd to the melicious directory
1. Run $ python createdb.py
2. Run $ nohup python ./melicious.py &
3. Aim your browser at http://localhost:8080/
4. Add and enjoy bookmarks

How do I stop?
==========================================
0. Kill the pid of the process running melicious.

What's under the hood?
==========================================
Bottle - http://bottle.paws.de/
SQLite3 - http://www.sqlite.org/

I have suggestions
==========================================
Contact brian@briantanaka.com

